Git 

Why Git:

Whenever you are working on any project , We have to manage our code in repository to avoid –
 
1.Code lost due to System Crash ,
2.Code loss due to by mistake Deleting the files
3.Git also makes collaboration easier
4.Allowing changes by multiple people to all be merged into one source. 

About Git:

